
head
  //- add page specific styles by appending to the head
  title="Quicklist"
  link(rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/index.css")
  //- add page specific js
  script(src="/javascripts/index.js" type="module" defer)

body
  nav
    span
    h1 Quicklist
    a.navButtons(href="/users/login") Login
  main
    content.main
      h3 Hello,
      h2 Welcome to Quicklist
      .buttons
        form(action='/users/login' method='post')
          input(type='hidden' name='_csrf' value=csrfToken)
          input(value=`${demoEmail}` name="email" type='hidden')
          input(value=`${demoPwd}` name="password" type='hidden')
          button.navButtons(type='submit' ) Demo
        a.navButtons(href="/users/signup") Signup
      p Quicklist is a remember the milk clone catered to programmers. Quicklist lets users create groups, add members and set tasks for members.  Try it out without creating an account by clicking the Demo button!
    img(src="./snippet1.PNG")
    img(src="/images/snippet1.png")
